descriptionHtml:
New, better Khajiit.  If the mod works, that is. 
This is a work in progress which could have problems. Best if used with S.A.M. 

Frankly, this upload is just to test the waters in making a mod!
I know the textures, animations, face .tri data work, but there's no knowing what could go wrong!
